  "instructions": [
    "Cook the rice noodles according to package instructions and set aside",
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute",
    "Stir in the tadka spice blend and cook for 30 seconds",
    "Add the chopped walnuts and cook until fragrant",
    "Add the cooked noodles, fish sauce, and lime juice to the skillet and stir to combine",
    "Season with salt to taste",
    "Serve immediately and garnish with additional walnuts if desired"
